{"data":{"Article":{"html":"<h2>What Can you do with The Slack Bot</h2>\n<p><strong>Search for Queries (Use the <code>/redash</code> slash command to search for Redash queries to add to the conversation.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/5877897f90336009736c5d9b/images/5a1c48972c7d3a272c0df9a2/file-VbAc93tixC.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>Embed Redash URLs - Convert Redash URLs in your conversation into rich embeds with preview of the visualization.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/5877897f90336009736c5d9b/images/5a1c4a81042863319924c7b4/file-D9EVKeW9IO.png\"></p>\n<h2>Setting up the Slack Bot</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Click on the <a href=\"https://redash.io/slack\">Add to Slack</a> link:\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/5877897f90336009736c5d9b/images/5a1c432e2c7d3a272c0df966/file-TQbF399E9U.png\"></li>\n<li>Once the bot is added to your Slack workspace, you'll get pinged by it to finish setup<br>\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/5877897f90336009736c5d9b/images/5a1c4476042863319924c774/file-GPUjLNs1gl.png\"></li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"permalink":null,"title":"Slack Bot (posting visualizations to Slack)","description":null,"keywords":null,"parent_category":"user-guide","category":"integrations-and-api","toc":null,"layout":null,"hide_topics":null},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"kb/user-guide/integrations-and-api/slack-bot-posting-visualizations-to-slack.md"}},"Parent":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Integrations and API"}},"Section":{"name":"User Guide"}},"pageContext":{"category":"integrations-and-api","parent_category":"user-guide","slug":"slack-bot-posting-visualizations-to-slack"}}